# csharp_desktop Profile

## Purpose

Use this profile for a C# desktop or local tool project with a solution/project structure and explicit build, test, and smoke entrypoints.

## Recommended Layout

- Solution or project files.
- src/ or project folders.
- docs/.
- Optional script entrypoints when implemented: build.ps1, test.ps1, smoke.ps1.

## Phase Gate

This profile expects a phase gate before implementation. Do not assume build/test/smoke commands exist until the target project defines them.

## P1 Boundary

This profile template does not create C# code, solution files, project files, or PowerShell scripts.

## Safety Notes

Do not include machine-specific paths, credentials, private inputs, or sensitive desktop data in docs or templates.
